{"tid":1649630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，請係適當時候，適當地方，做適合的事","createTime":"2019-10-12T17:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T07:03:59.000Z","uid":81236,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"344e89a71e42579d54e4dcd7841cc903c3f77e1d","tid":1649630,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:39:21.000Z","msg":"經歷左呢幾個月，幾乎每日都有新既悲劇發生<br />\n<br />\n以為香港人已經進步左，知道咩時候要做咩事<br />\n<br />\n但估唔到居然係太子站外慶祝生日...唔講我以為已經贏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/72662499_138280374189252_780526786113961984_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_oc=AQlBEq6NiGkkQzhG1UvMPacBSEGD3q3TtyKcB0prt9AtrOAG3TNV8ng0p3r8v8CYUFo&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=53eaeed311640232472e10ea319fc359&amp;oe=5E258AD5\" /><br />\n<br />\n你知唔知岩岩先有兩個手足係果到比人捉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底知唔知太子站係一個悲劇既地方<br />\n<br />\n雖然抗爭中有點歡樂可以調和一下心理<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但請係適當時地，做適當的事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔會同你地割，但希望大家可以改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請香港人團結一心，我有預感港共政權會順住不停加入嘉年元揀<br />\n<br />\n對抗極權，快樂無憂抗爭絕對唔係一條出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有打敗極權，先可以得快真正無自由既快樂"},{"pid":"66e09ef47c6ebc86bb562aae171b821f40b299d4","tid":1649630,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69193a1d3dc8a8434abe0a77279629ed1b75095","tid":1649630,"uid":149349,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:43:01.000Z","msg":"想提提大家，我地輸左既後果，怕你地唔記得<br />\n//2年內：<br />\n逃犯條例修訂重啟 通過<br />\n23條 通過<br />\n國歌法 通過<br />\n辱警罪 通過<br />\n被捕人士數量因秋後算賬大搜捕而大量上升<br />\n被捕人士相繼罪成 判贏5-10年監禁<br />\n<br />\n5年內：<br />\n取消中文聆聽及說話科 及後強制普通話為必修科<br />\n開始封禁FB IG GOOGLE YOUTUBE等網站<br />\n增加每日來港中國人人數<br />\n全體官員及警察大幅加薪<br />\n<br />\n15年內：<br />\n建一教育營 再教育香港異見人士<br />\n將警察編入為公安一部門<br />\n在港實施中國法律<br />\n取消邊境關口"},{"pid":"1fa7ae57b9fef65c77a91689a56074cc1acfcee3","tid":1649630,"uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:43:20.000Z","msg":"生日果個而家係咪好快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你知唔知你既一時快樂可以係建築係無數人既痛苦之上"},{"pid":"1f466e597024e619f494c17f585602f4e29bccbd","tid":1649630,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:43:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d1838f9dd87e20f7e3d10df4b90792273d1ef471","tid":1649630,"uid":29581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:44:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZubvzTs9uJ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZubvzTs9uJ4&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9lT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=1f304b19\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZubvzTs9uJ4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又係時候要聽下呢首歌</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea249add6ea78afe6dadb3ece10f671b1bb453e3","tid":1649630,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:44:32.000Z","msg":"係戰場慶祝生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc564707a2e905c78e6adb018c477beff7c4ea91","tid":1649630,"uid":30476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a69193a1d3dc8a8434abe0a77279629ed1b75095","tid":1649630,"uid":149349,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T17:43:01.000Z","msg":"想提提大家，我地輸左既後果，怕你地唔記得<br />\n//2年內：<br />\n逃犯條例修訂重啟 通過<br 